label: OfferActivity
text: Refund policy: any point of time cancelled by user or unable to delivery on time full amount will be refunded to the same account Do you need to TIP our delivery executives? Please don’t. We don’t want to be a one-time player like other food apps rather we would like to focus on affordability for our daily consumption. If any of us asks for any favour please refuse and intimate us Immediately. As a courtesy we shall refund you the order value to the next nearest 100Rs (ex: If your order is 101Rs we refund 200Rs) or 500Rs whichever is less. Modes of payment? Our objective is to support our governments digital drive. However due to administrative reasons we accept CASH and UPI payments only. Our technical team is working round-the-clock to match your expectations. What areas are we serving? To ensure Quality/Hygiene/Affordability we are operating only in HSR Layout (Bangalore) and Kelambakkam Siruseri IT park (Chennai). As and when we see these 3 parameters satisfied we plan to expand to BTM Madiwala (Bangalore) by Apr’17. Disclaimer and refund
